    "workflow_engine",
    "runtime_manifest",
    "transition_authority",
    "truth_registry"
  ],
  "map_rules": [
    "entries are derived from already frozen contracts, schemas, docs, and supporting surfaces",
    "requires_surfaces and enables_surfaces record dependency and discoverability relationships only; they do not authorize execution",
    "follow_on_route_surface may be null or domain_gateway only",
    "canonical truth remains in governing OPL contracts and in domain systems rather than in this lifecycle map",
    "candidate backlog entries may expose blocked admission dependencies, but they do not authorize automatic promotion or routing"
